{"id": "10161", "post": "<div class=\"post-10161 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-portugal\" id=\"post-10161\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lusovps-new-kvm-xen/\" rel=\"bookmark\">LusoVPS.com \u2013 New KVM and Xen Packages starting at $3.51/month!</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/portugal/\" rel=\"tag\">portugal</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> February 28, 2017 @ 3:00 am, by Matt Zelasko</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.lusovps.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIyMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMjAwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/lusovps.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\"></a></p><p>Filipe just sent this offer over and we\u2019re happy to feature <a href=\"https://www.lusovps.com/\" target=\"_blank\">LusoVPS</a> once again. This is their second time being posted and this is a pretty good one. LusoVPS has been providing VPS services since 2011. Their WHOIS is public, and they\u2019re a registered company (VAT Registration Number is: PT510699332) in Povoa de Varzim, Oporto, Portugal.</p><p>You can find their <a href=\"https://www.lusovps.com/files/terms.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">legal docs here.</a></p><p>They accept PayPal, major credit cards, and wire transfers. They also accept Multibanco within Portugal.</p><p><strong>A note from Filipe:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>\u201cWe\u2019ve started with Xen-Only with success and we\u2019re now implementing KVM virtualization side by side with Xen to fullfil our customer needs. By being a Xen-only provider up until now, we\u2019re&nbsp;confident that we will be able to provide the same quality service on this new Virtualization by applying our tech knowledge and our server managing skills.\u201d</em></p><p><strong>Here are the offers:</strong></p><table style=\"height: 265px\" width=\"650\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>KVM Package</strong><p></p><ul><li>2GB RAM</li><li>2x vCPU</li><li>75GB HDD space</li><li>2TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: LEBANDLUSO</li><li>6\u20ac/month ~= $6.39/month</li><li>[<a href=\"https://cart.lusovps.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=132&amp;carttpl=slider\" target=\"_blank\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Xen VPS (PV and HVM) Package</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>256MB Swap (Doesn\u2019t apply for HVM)</li><li>1x vCPU</li><li>10GB HDD space</li><li>1TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>/112 IPv6 (65535 IPv6 addresses)</li><li>Xen/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: LEBANDLUSO</li><li>3.30\u20ac/month ~= $3.51/month</li><li>[<a href=\"https://cart.lusovps.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=6&amp;carttpl=slider\" target=\"_blank\">(PV) Order Now</a>]</li><li>[<a href=\"https://cart.lusovps.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=7&amp;carttpl=slider\" target=\"_blank\">(HVM) Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>Network Info:</strong><span id=\"more-10161\"></span></p><div><b>For the KVM service, the servers are located here:</b><br>\nHetzner DC 13 \u2013 Nuremberg, Germany</div><div>Test IPv4: 213.133.100.125<br>\nTest IPv6: 2a01:4f8:130:5085::2<br>\nTest file: <a href=\"http://213.133.100.125/200mb.test\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://213.133.100.125/200mb.test</a><b>For the Xen service, the servers are located here:</b><br>\nOVH \u2013 Roubaix, France</div><div>Test IPv4: 37.187.249.142<br>\nTest IPv6: 2001:1af8:4020:a053:1::1<br>\nTest file:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://37.187.249.142/200mb.test\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://37.187.249.142/200mb.test</a></div><div><b>Node Specification \u2013 KVM</b><br>\n\u2013 1x Intel Xeon i7-3930K CPU @ 3.20GHz<br>\n\u2013 64GB RAM<br>\n\u2013 4x 2TB HDDs<br>\n\u2013 Software RAID10<br>\n\u2013 1Gbps uplink<b>Node Specification \u2013 XEN</b><br>\n\u2013 1x Intel Xeon E5-1620 v2 @ 3.70GHz<br>\n\u2013 64GB RAM<br>\n\u2013 2x 2TB HDDs<br>\n\u2013 Software RAID1<br>\n\u2013 1Gbps uplink</div><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flusovps-new-kvm-xen%2F&amp;t=LusoVPS.com%20-%20New%20KVM%20and%20Xen%20Packages%20starting%20at%20%243.51%2Fmonth%21\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=LusoVPS.com%20-%20New%20KVM%20and%20Xen%20Packages%20starting%20at%20%243.51%2Fmonth%21&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flusovps-new-kvm-xen%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Fl